title: Profile Builder Pro 2.9.0 - WordPress Profile Plugin
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org To achieve this, just create a new page, and give it an intuitive name (i.e. Edit Profile). Now all you need to do is add the following shortcode: [wppb-edit-profile]. Publish your page and you are done! Profile Builder Pro WordPress Plugin is the all in one user registration and management plugin for WordPress sites. Scroll down to see why. Profile Builder Pro WordPress Plugin Features Use On Unlimited Sites Login, Register and Edit Profile Shortcodes Manage Default User Fields Minimum Password Length & Strength Admin Approval & Email Confirmation Unlimited Extra User Fields Conditional Logic for Fields Avatar Upload For Users reCaptcha Support
